00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:03,359
on our import and export business.

361
00:20:03,800 --> 00:20:05,239
Learn from him.

362
00:20:05,239 --> 00:20:06,375
Be humble.

363
00:20:06,925 --> 00:20:07,560
I will.

