374
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,439
in Hangzhou.

375
00:20:52,175 --> 00:20:53,119
Who was that?

376
00:20:55,075 --> 00:20:56,880
Some social butterfly, I guess.

377
00:20:58,250 --> 00:20:59,359
They couldn't

378
00:20:59,550 --> 00:21:00,640
