455
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:24,750
Mmm.

456
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:26,481
It's good.

457
00:24:27,525 --> 00:24:28,606
Thank you.

458
00:24:42,950 --> 00:24:45,310
